feedback_meta.text:
-= Kitchen =-
You find yourself in a kitchen. An usual one. You begin looking for stuff.

You can see an opened conventional looking fridge in the room. The fridge is empty, what a horrible day! You see a gleam over in a corner, where you can see an oven. You can make out a table. The table is massive. On the table you make out a cookbook. You see a gleam over in a corner, where you can see a counter. You see a knife on the counter. You see a stove. But the thing is empty, unfortunately.

There is an open sliding patio door leading east. There is an open plain door leading south. There is an exit to the north. Don't worry, there is no door.
